data.name: oracleSelectCommand2.CommandText
data.value: SELECT d.ID_DISCIPLINE, d.ID_GROUP, get_discname_with_groupname(d.ID_DISCNAME, d.ID_GROUP) AS DISCNAME FROM DISCIPLINES d, TEACHERS2DISCIPLINES td, TEACHERS t WHERE d.ID_DISCIPLINE = td.DISCIPLINES_ID_DISCIPLINE AND td.TEACHERS_ID_TEACHER = t.ID_TEACHER AND (t.ID_TEACHER = :tid)

data.name: oracleUpdateCommand2.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE "DISCIPLINES" SET "ID_DISCIPLINE" = :ID_DISCIPLINE, "ID_GROUP" = :ID_GROUP WHERE (("ID_DISCIPLINE" = :Original_ID_DISCIPLINE) AND ((:IsNull_ID_GROUP = 1 AND "ID_GROUP" IS NULL) OR ("ID_GROUP" = :Original_ID_GROUP)))

data.name: oracleSelectCommand5.CommandText
data.value: SELECT m.id_mark, m.value_mark, m.date_mark, get_fullname(s.last_name, s.first_name, s.third_name) AS FULLNAME FROM marks m JOIN students s ON s.id_student = m.id_student WHERE (m.id_teacher = :tid) AND (m.id_discipline = :did)

data.name: oracleUpdateCommand5.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE "MARKS" SET "ID_MARK" = :ID_MARK, "VALUE_MARK" = :VALUE_MARK, "DATE_MARK" = :DATE_MARK WHERE (("ID_MARK" = :Original_ID_MARK) AND ((:IsNull_VALUE_MARK = 1 AND "VALUE_MARK" IS NULL) OR ("VALUE_MARK" = :Original_VALUE_MARK)) AND ((:IsNull_DATE_MARK = 1 AND "DATE_MARK" IS NULL) OR ("DATE_MARK" = :Original_DATE_MARK)))

data.name: oracleDeleteCommand5.CommandText
data.value: DELETE FROM "MARKS" WHERE (("ID_MARK" = :Original_ID_MARK) AND ((:IsNull_VALUE_MARK = 1 AND "VALUE_MARK" IS NULL) OR ("VALUE_MARK" = :Original_VALUE_MARK)) AND ((:IsNull_DATE_MARK = 1 AND "DATE_MARK" IS NULL) OR ("DATE_MARK" = :Original_DATE_MARK)))
